profile: Capital Home Staging & Design is currently Ottawa's only award winning home staging company taking home the 2009 BBB Torch award for Marketplace ethics. We have a team of educated and dedicated professional stagers whom are ready to help home owners maximize the value of their home in the most cost effective way.
service_area: Ottawa and all surrounding areas (Rockland to Smith Falls and beyond)
services: Professional Home Staging Consultations, Colour Consultations, Interior Redesign.
brands: we work with ICI, Benjamin Moore, and Sherwin Williams paint decks.
specialities: We specialize in home staging helping home owners address their home so it appeals to the most amount of buyers in the lease amount of time, from furniture placement to possible upgrades we can do it all.
payment_method: We accept cash, cheque, and credit card processed through paypal. No account is needed.
diplomas:
All from Quality Course Design School.
-ISRP International Staging & Redesign Professional.
-IOP I
memberships:
RESA -Real Estate Staging Association.
BBC -Business Breakfast Club
warranty_terms: We have contracts for clients that require additional services over the initial consultation.
